      "originalText": "GET  /tasks   (show all task created by particular user)\nGET  /tasks?status=todo && priorty=high   (show )\nGET  /task/:taskid   (show single task of user with assigned user with collabulators)\nGET  /assigned-tasks (Get all assigned task)\nGET  /invite/collaburates (Get all task in which i have to collaburate)\nGET  /task/collaburates (in which i am collaburates)\n",
